pullrequest.title: Do not export urdf symbols in sdformat 1.4 (-> sdf_1.4)

content.raw: Being totally intuitive (sorry no deeper understanding of symbol generation) I would say that most of them come from classes using templates which at any point are instantiated using urdf classes. I believe that the point is not to find URDF symbols coming from urdf files, like class declarations (look for Sphere, Vecto3r, etc).
